properties.Name: Ukrainian Kharkiv Counterattack
properties.descriptio: Counteroffensive started 6th September 2022 until it stabilised in December 2022. Based on geolocated troop positions and assessments. This polygon covers the area recaptured by Ukraine, plus any incremental adjustments during 2023 and 2024

properties.Name: Ukrainian Kherson Counterattack
properties.descriptio: Began in late August 2022 as a feint to draw units away from Kharkiv. Then large movements began 1st October, until major advances started on 7th November because Russia was retreating from Kherson west bank. Finished by 11/11/22

properties.Name: Initial Invasion Kyiv Axis
properties.descriptio: Russian forces invaded Ukraine from the north east in an attempt to take Kyiv on February 24th 2022 until they were repulsed by 2nd April 2022

properties.Name: Ukraine Kharkiv Counterattack 2024
properties.descriptio: From May 2024, to repel the Russian forces invading from the north

properties.Name: Disputed Area - Kursk
properties.descriptio: Claims and geolocations from both sides have this area as unknown control. We just don't have enough information
